::Havoc/Repressor::

Havoc swears as the ship he and his group was on shakes, the computer 
reporting more damage.

"Return fire! Evasive manuevers!" he yells. Repressor, the pilot, initiates 
the complex manuevers, wading out of more shots coming at the ship.

He and his group were criminals, on the run from Maximal Police. They had 
spent the last few years destroying Maximal facilities, and had recently 
gotten cornered by Maximal police.
